sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant C as 客户端
    participant G as API Gateway
    participant A as Go 接入服务
    participant R as Redis
    participant M as RocketMQ
    participant O as 订单消费者
    participant P as PostgreSQL
    participant Q as 查询服务

    C->>G: POST /seckill(request_id)
    G->>G: 鉴权、资格、限流、防重放
    G->>A: 转发请求

    A->>A: 生成 reservation_id、message_id
    A->>R: Lua 原子预占
    R-->>A: RESERVED

    A->>M: 发送 OrderCreateRequested
    M-->>A: Broker ACK

    A->>R: best effort 标记 MESSAGE_SENT
    A-->>C: HTTP 202 / QUEUED

    M->>O: 投递消息
    O->>P: BEGIN

    O->>P: INSERT consumer_inbox
    O->>P: 领取 inventory_token
    O->>P: INSERT orders
    O->>P: INSERT inventory_reservation
    O->>P: INSERT inventory_ledger
    O->>P: INSERT event_outbox

    O->>P: COMMIT
    O-->>M: ACK

    O->>R: 更新 ORDER_CREATED 查询状态

    C->>Q: GET /seckill/result
    Q->>R: 查询 request_id / reservation_id
    R-->>Q: ORDER_CREATED + order_id
    Q-->>C: 返回订单结果
